{
  "texts": [
    "Prompt Engineering & Vocabulary Tokenization.",
    "LLMs can behave sensitively concerning the specific context construction.",
    "This has led to terms such as 'prompt engineering'.",
    "Throughout our investigations, we consider various prompt construction approaches to provide ablative insights into the underlying LLM mechanisms.",
    "More specifically and motivated by computational resource considerations, we conduct coordinate-wise evaluations in order to extract a well-performing approach."
  ]
}